-   Farmer information and crop data are protected under applicable data protection laws
-   Market price predictions and recommendations are provided as-is without warranty

### Export Compliance

-   This software may be subject to export control laws
-   Agricultural technology and ML models may have specific export restrictions
-   Users are responsible for compliance with local and international laws

